snippet.textDisplay:
❤️❤️❤️ I've loved this song earlier too, but today felt it 💯, 
🥺🥺😭😭😭
 my baby sparrow ( I rescued her from the dog , one leg & wing got injured so she's with me ,i was treating her, she learned to fly little, so I was listening this song from last week because I kept it free- freedom is everybody's right, so anytime she can fly away to her destination wherever she wants..
 but even after treating her, taking to vet , pampering her- her leg wasn't healing & also respiratory problems (dog almost bit her).. she took her last breath today early morning 😭😭😭
She loved music, whenever I played my instruments- flute, ukulele, harmonium.. she came near to me, on me.. she's so beautiful, loveliest😘🥰😘.. ❤️❤️❤️ 
I already felt like her momma, she loved my company too🥰🥰, 
Mari jode j aavi jay, we ate together, played, watched webseries, listened & sang songs,took a bath, slept..all together..
  but she left..🥺🥺😭😭😭😭😭😭😭 
I love you my bachchu always & forever 😘😘❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️💖💖💕💕
RIP my chirping kiddo💖❤️💐🥺🥺😭😭😭...
